name: "Eater" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Digital drawing created with a no-longer-supported, free app on my Samsung Galaxy phone.] This artificially created entity was intended to consume plastics and other "waste" products...but something went wrong. For some reason, it has decided that HUMANS are waste, and is happy to consume them, as well! ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
